# Time Series Forecasting

This project performs time series forecasting using the STL (Seasonal and Trend decomposition using Loess) method.

## Installation

1. Clone the repository: `git clone https://github.com/danilekuruch/forecasting.git`
2. Install the required dependencies: `pip install -r requirements.txt`

## Usage

1. Ensure you have a CSV file with the time series data.
2. Run the main script: `python main.py --path ../test/Video_Games_Sales_as_at_22_Dec_2016.csv --ts-name NA_Sales --ts-index 0 --ts-length 200 --forecast-steps 5`

